```plantuml
@startuml hypertrack_live-app-android

actor User
participant "LiveApp" as A
participant "CognitoClient" as B
participant "HyperTrack SDK" as C
participant "Backend API" as D
participant "Google Maps" as E
participant "GeofenceApiAdapter" as F
participant "DeepLinkHandler" as G

User -> A: Open App
A -> B: Authenticate User
B --> A: Authentication Token

A -> C: Start Location Sharing
C -> D: Create Trip
D --> C: Trip Details

A -> E: Display Map
E --> A: Show User Location

User -> F: Set Home Geofence
F --> A: Geofence Set

User -> G: Open Deep Link
G --> A: Process Deep Link

User -> A: Share Location Link
A -> D: Generate Invite Link
D --> A: Invite Link

User -> A: Stop Location Sharing
A -> C: Complete Trip
C -> D: Update Trip Status
D --> C: Confirmation

@enduml
```